    public interface AclfBranchResultRec
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Aclf Branch Result Rec'. AclfBranchResultRec is used for recording the branch result and the branch result summary. Branch summary result is used for storing summary of multiple study cases, for example, in security margin analysis.

    The following features are supported:

    • Desc
    • PFlow
    • QFlow
    • Mva Flow
    • Mva Loading Percent
    • Amps Flow
    • Amps Loading Percent
    • Rating
